<br />\n同香港01就話《環球時報》的報道正確<br />\n<br />\nTVB確認《環時》報道 對港媒書面回應刪「打壓」「成磨心」字句<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/350461/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F350461%2F&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3XXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=30b6d308\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/350461/</a>"},{"pid":"2a7d0df4d34524a64fc8a892549788cde3a3a19a","tid":1304430,"uid":128648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"［我想置頂］希望大家入黎望下，想留意返大家嘅風向去左邊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304350</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"05991fd6d8d7c1338903eda2e130942f0c2fe948","tid":1304430,"uid":15696,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2014/03/26/32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2014%2F03%2F26%2F32.jpg&h=05aeeeb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e4ce506a41886fe7edeeafdd6442d797652cf42","tid":1304430,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:19:02.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"b807fb97b909483f8f11212a1f1825c285378179","tid":1304430,"uid":15696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:20:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">TVB已經表哂態  7/28你唔係唔出嚟呀?</span></span>"},{"pid":"33318e3172d9d896277c5029e9bccb05c1c16caa","tid":1304430,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:21:34.000Z","msg":"任何對無綫電視不恰當的打壓，均不會影響本台公正不偏、客觀持平的新聞報道原則。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TVB：任何的打壓，均不會影響本台的新聞原則</span>"},{"pid":"526c7aa205537c418a0a01ba3982e00cf8098c66","tid":1304430,"uid":68366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:24:21.000Z","msg":"抵制香港